ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR PERFORMANCE DATA:

The performance data (CSV files in /data directory) is released into the
PUBLIC DOMAIN. You may use, modify, distribute, and build upon this data
for any purpose without restriction or attribution.

The purpose is complete transparency and independent verification of all
performance claims made by ClaudeHedge.

