PROPRIETARY TRADING PARAMETERS:

This license does NOT include proprietary trading parameters, specific
position sizing values, or exact conditional expansion formulas. Those
remain confidential trade secrets and are NOT part of this repository.

What IS shared under this license:
✓ Framework architecture and methodology
✓ Performance data (complete transparency)
✓ Risk management framework
✓ Backtesting code and infrastructure
✓ Data pipeline and analytics tools
✓ Visualization and reporting tools

What is NOT shared (proprietary IP):
✗ Exact position sizing percentages
✗ Specific entry/exit signal algorithms
✗ Proprietary indicator parameters
✗ Conditional expansion formulas
✗ VIX threshold values

This approach follows the philosophy of "show the results, protect the edge."

